#      Tierrafr√≠a, V. H. et al. (2022). RegulonDB 11.0: Comprehensive high-throughput datasets on transcriptional regulation in Escherichia coli K-12,
# Genome version: U00096.3, Refseq version: NC_000913.3; GI:556503834
# (1) pmId. Promoter identifier assigned by RegulonDB
# (3) strand. DNA strand where the promoter is located
# (4) posTSS. Genome map position of Transcription Start Site (+1)
# (5) sigmaF. Sigma Factor that recognize the promoter
# (7) pmEvidence. Evidence that supports the existence of the promoter
# (9) confidenceLevel. Promoter confidence level (Values: Confirmed, Strong, Weak)
